{"tid":314143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"凌志撞壆翻側沙瀝半粒鐘兩車禍","createTime":"2017-07-09T02:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T02:33:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"59e06a097bdaccb2a6a13845ef705096cb761832","tid":314143,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:33:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20083956&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170709\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20083956%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170709&d=9K4m331hoOOF5Vr9VFkABZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=f68ba945\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20083956%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170709&h=33ddaa47\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20083956&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170709</a><br />\n<br />\n凌志撞壆翻側<br />\n沙瀝半粒鐘兩車禍<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】沙田沙瀝公路中午發生兩宗車禍，共5人受傷。昨日中午12時20分左右，一輛白色凌志私家車沙瀝公路行駛，至威爾斯醫院對開天橋上失控，撞壆翻側，車上1男1女受輕傷。20多分鐘後，現場後方約200米處，一輛AUDI房車被福士房車撞向其尾部，意外中3人受輕傷。"}]}